Major', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/150922/', '', 'Viloxazine', 'Nitrous oxide, Desflurane, Enflurane, Esketamine, Halothane, Etomidate', 1767369485);
